body:
Page 29: 
- Hmm!! Another work strangely well done.
So it was insect version of hitch cool.

It was a nice comic overall, but those bugs are freaking NIGHTMARE fuel.

just think about a terrifying bug the size of a cat sneaking up behind you with a 4-inch stinger

That...went better than expected. 
And by better than expected, I mean boy meets girl, boy fucks girl, instead of 'monster gets meat'.
Was totally expecting 'Monster gets Meat'.
